_sText: CS:S ports of bhop_smth, bhop_tanker2, and bhop_behomeby10.

Hello! These are my first set of bunny hop maps I've made over the past couple of weeks! They're all around 30-40 seconds  to speedrun. On the heaven one if you see the skybox as an error turn down your settings. (I dunno why it does that...)

Making maps is new to me and I plan on making bigger and better maps in the future, so any feedback that can be given would be greatly appreciated!


I probably forgot to credit someone, so sorry about that D:

I wanted to try and get a community map pack together, a map from each mapper, but a lot of the people I asked weren't up for it and a few of those who were bailed or decided to upload theirs individually, so I'm just dropping the maps I've recieved so far here since I cba to deal with trying to get more mappers involved + I'm working on a bigger project that I want to channel all my free time into.

This pack consists of 5 maps;
bhop_spyro by Benchmarked (The map is a model so it was aids to trigger sorry) - stafe map - 20s main map, 10s bonus
bhop_askowo by Benchmarked - strafe/slightly technichal map - 50+ s main map, 45+sÂ  bonus.
bhop_nalliexkaren - Short fly map with another 45-50s bonus.
bhop_spution by Flow - Short strafe map
bhop_flydown by Soda - Short fly map

Thanks to those who contributed, and to those who at least tried to, hope y'all enjoy some of these.

This is a collection of 15 maps both re-created, original and ports.
I do NOT own any of the following maps, but I am the sole porter of the files that are contained in the archive:
bhop_avantura_fixed - 15-30~ sec, medium strafe map
bhop_d3stiny_3 <15 second extremely short strafe map
bhop_darkstars >30 second non-strafe map, technical/routing
bhop_die <15 second short strafe map with a technical aspect that can be skipped
bhop_hb_cobrex <20 semi-short strafe map
bhop_m_snow_fixed <20 technical map with ladder
bhop_miojo <25s pure strafe map with surf
bhop_movementkrueppel <5 extremely short strafe map, similiar to freedompuppies
bhop_platinum_lol <1min very technical kz/bhop map with slopes, ladders, kz and technical turns
bhop_pro_bhop_1 <10s strafe map with technical climb end that can be skipped
bhop_purplehop <20s strafe map
bhop_quickbhop <20s general bhop map with technical climb end

bhop_floating_objects_remake is an original created by Acer. I never intended it to be played on most servers, nor did Acer probably, as it's an experimental map and not natively bhop, but can still be played like a bhop map.

Most of these maps were never uploaded due to either laziness, or just unwillingness to do so, but are all playable. Most maps contained wherein are short, <15 second maps, so keep that in mind before you dump them all onto your server if you dislike short, strafe maps.
Maps all ported or created by me, enjoy.

DISCLAIMER: If any of the original mappers has an issue with any of these maps being distributed freely to this website, contact me and I'll have the maps removed.

_sText:
Another collection of maps ported within the past 6~ months by me and a friend.
All of these maps should be playable on any style except bhop_kz_imanoob which is strictly for auto. And bhop_gsbq has a "secret" room for people who try to skip the map entirely.

Maps:
bhop_bkz_aztecbhop
bhop_gsbq
bhop_kz_imanoob
bhop_placements_v3
bhop_rainbow_cs

If you run into any issues, leave a comment and they will be addressed accordingly.
If any of the original authors has an issue with us releasing your map, please leave a comment or message us and we will take it down ASAP no questions asked.

Here's another collection of maps ported from 1.6 bhop/kz, to the source engine on CS:S. The following maps may still have some issues, but at the time this was the best we could do for some of these maps as some of these date before we fully figured out vertex alignment/lmp file corruption.
If some of the errors seem off-putting, just know we wouldn't release any map if it was completely bugged, or broken/unplayable.

As always by the way to the original authors, PLEASE let us know if you don't want us re-distributing your map on this website, we will take it down IMMEDIATELY.

_sText:
**UPDATE**

- Balanced stage 7 (white blocks in the climbing sections are checkpoints, some parts are a bit easier)
- Reduced the first 256 unit longjump in stage 2 to 242
- Minor optimization on stages 1 and 8
- Fixed a teleport glitch on stage 3

This map was designed with the limitations of sv_enablebunnyhopping 0 and legit gameplay in mind, meaning you are not be able to maintain a speed above 300 while bunnyhopping, forcing you to strafe in order to complete the map. It may not play properly on servers with settings other than what it was made for, such as autobunnyhopping or forcing sv_enablebunnyopping back to 1.

For servers, visit http://steamcommunity.com/groups/_strafe

**kz_bhop_sakura**

kz_bhop_sakura is intended to be played EXCLUSIVELY on legit normal difficulty 100 tick servers that force sv_airaccelerate 100, fps_max 300, sv_gravity 800 and no scout. Since this map was designed mostly with single jump normal legit game play in mind, it is extremely easy on easy/auto settings. To experience this map how it was meant to be played, visit one of the following servers.

- fap ~ 85.131.192.94:29681
- bhop.it bhop ~ 94.75.251.224:27017
- bhop.it lj ~ 94.75.251.224:27016
- aus elite bhop ~ 119.252.191.48:27085
- l2scroll or die trying ~ 95.172.92.5:27015

This is the first map I have ever made. I know some of you don't like Dev textures but I personally think it looks amazing with good lighting, awesome shadows and some simple abstract designs so IceTiger and I have done our best to make it as aesthetically pleasing as possible.
All the game play was done by me. IceTiger did all of the abstract designs and lamp creations. Working with IceTiger was really fun and he had so many great ideas we got to implement and also has a vast knowledge of hammer which helped so much.

The biggest thanks to Badges for helping me with hammer and every problem i had. Could not have been done without him.

The second biggest thanks to sp/a/rx for creating awesome line art, sprites and the ladder texture for me with his professional Photoshop skills =).

Last but not least thank you to everyone who tested my map for me so i could make the game play as good as possible, again map couldn't have been done without you!

Enjoy.
